**story**
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey resided in a Jamun tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife.
The monkey wanted to make a cloth for himsef from the crocodile skin. He slowly started trying to befriend the crocodile by feeding him the berries. The berries were so delicious and the crocodile liked it. After some time, the monkey started poisoning the berries
